Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:30.71,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}鎖のよう連なる 絡み合う宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:30.71,OP_CH,NTP,440,0,0,,{\blur2\an2\fs24}カルマ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:36.93,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}白金で断つ運命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:36.93,OP_CH,NTP,0,200,0,,{\blur2\an2\fs24}ひかり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:36.93,OP_CH,NTP,200,0,0,,{\blur2\an2\fs24}さだめ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:40.74,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}Stand up! Stand up! Stand up!
